tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE QuantumExecutionTime (
   algorithm_id INT,
   execution_time DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Performance_Optimization (
    optimization_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    optimization_technique VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    execution_time FLOAT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES Quantum_Algorithms(algorithm_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT NOT NULL,
    execution_time DECIMAL(10,3),
    result_data TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES Quantum_Algorithms (algorithm_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Optimization (
    optimization_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT NOT NULL,
    optimization_technique VARCHAR(100),
    optimization_time DECIMAL(10,3),
    FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES Quantum_Algorithms (algorithm_id)
);

CREATE TABLE executions (
    execution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    start_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    end_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    algorithm_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_algorithm_id FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES quantum_algorithms (algorithm_id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_user_id FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users (user_id)
);
